echo "The sensors-detect script is not included in the CPUstress image."
echo "The kernel used by CPUstress has all hardware monitoring drivers built-in, so"
echo "the 'sensors' program should have detected all sensors on your system."
echo "If not, please report the missing drivers on the Ultimate Boot CD forums."
echo "<http://www.ultimatebootcd.com/forums/>"
